{"schema_version":"1.7.3","id":"OESA-2022-1612","published":"2022-04-12T11:03:42Z","modified":"2025-09-03T06:17:52.099684Z","upstream":["CVE-2022-0547"],"summary":"openvpn security update","details":"OpenVPN can be extended through the --plugin option, which provides possibilities to add specialized authentication, user accounting, packet filtering and related features. These plug-ins need to be written in C and provides a more low-level and information rich access to similar features as the various script-hooks.\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\r\n\r\nOpenVPN 2.1 until v2.4.12 and v2.5.6 may enable authentication bypass in external authentication plug-ins when more than one of them makes use of deferred authentication replies, which allows an external user to be granted access with only partially correct credentials.(CVE-2022-0547)","affected":[{"package":{"name":"openvpn","ecosystem":"openEuler:20.03-LTS-SP1","purl":"pkg:rpm/openEuler/openvpn&distro=openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP1"},"ranges":[{"type":"ECOSYSTEM","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"2.4.8-8.oe1"}]}],"ecosystem_specific":{"aarch64":["openvpn-2.4.8-8.oe1.aarch64.rpm","openvpn-devel-2.4.8-8.oe1.aarch64.rpm","openvpn-debuginfo-2.4.8-8.oe1.aarch64.rpm","openvpn-debugsource-2.4.8-8.oe1.aarch64.rpm"],"noarch":["openvpn-help-2.4.8-8.oe1.noarch.rpm"],"src":["openvpn-2.4.8-8.oe1.src.rpm"],"x86_64":["openvpn-debuginfo-2.4.8-8.oe1.x86_64.rpm","openvpn-devel-2.4.8-8.oe1.x86_64.rpm","openvpn-2.4.8-8.oe1.x86_64.rpm","openvpn-debugsource-2.4.8-8.oe1.x86_64.rpm"]},"database_specific":{"source":"https://repo.openeuler.org/security/data/osv/OESA-2022-1612.json"}},{"package":{"name":"openvpn","ecosystem":"openEuler:20.03-LTS-SP2","purl":"pkg:rpm/openEuler/openvpn&distro=openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP2"},"ranges":[{"type":"ECOSYSTEM","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"2.4.8-8.oe1"}]}],"ecosystem_specific":{"aarch64":["openvpn-2.4.8-8.oe1.aarch64.rpm","openvpn-devel-2.4.8-8.oe1.aarch64.rpm","openvpn-debuginfo-2.4.8-8.oe1.aarch64.rpm","op